Interface WeightCalculator

    • Method Detail

      • getWeight

        double getWeight(Plan indivPlan,
                 ReplanningGroup replanningGroup)
        Defines the weight of a plan, used for selection. The method is called once for each plan: it is not required that the method returns the same result if called twice with the same arguments (ie it can return a random number).
        Parameters:
        indivPlan - the plan to weight
        replanningGroup - the group for which plans are being selected. Selectors using "niching" measures may need this. No modifications should be done to the group.
